Meta.DisplayName=Fika Headless Client
Meta.Description=Fika dedicated headless EFT client (runs under Wine) that registers with an existing SPT v4.0+ / Fika server. Bind-mount the EFT client folder to /opt/tarkov via CustomMountBinds after deployment.
Meta.OS=Linux
Meta.AarchSupport=NotSupported
Meta.Arch=x86_64
Meta.Author=Stress-CG
Meta.URL=https://wiki.project-fika.com/advanced-features/headless-client
